doctype html
html(lang='en')
  head
    meta(charset='UTF-8')
    meta(http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible' content='IE=edge')
    meta(name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
    title Jivescribe
  body
    div(style='font-family: Sans-Serif; max-width: 500px; border-top: 20px solid #0050b1; border-bottom: 20px solid #0050b1; padding: 15px;')
      div
        div(style='align-items: center; width: 50%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;')
          img(style='display: block; width: 250px; height: auto; align-self: center;' src='https://i.imgur.com/HAixGVj.png')
      div
        h3(style='width: 100%; text-align: center; color: #000;') Welcome to Jivescribe!
      div
        p(style='color: #000; ') You have been invited to be a staff member of Jivescribe.
      div
        p(style='color: #000;')
          | Accepting the invitation will activate the account we've created for you. This will allow you to collaborate and work with the Jivescribe Team.
      div
        p(style='color: #000;')
          | Please use the attached credentials. Once activated and logged in, you may update and change the password associated with your account.
      div
        div
          p(style='margin-bottom: 0;') Email: 
            span(style='color: #e67143;') #{email}
          p(style='margin-top: 0;') Password:
            span(style='color: #e67143;') #{password}
      div
        div(style='padding: 24px 0; text-align: center;')
          a(style='padding: 10px 16px; color: #ffffff; background-color: #0050b1; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;' href=link)  Accept Staff Invitation
      div
        div(style='display: block; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px; border-top: #a8a5a5 solid 2px; margin-top: 10px;')
          div
            p(style='color: #a8a5a5; text-align: center; font-size: 12px;')
              span(style='color: #a8a5a5; text-align: center; font-size: 12px;') Need assistance? Email us 
              span(style='color: #e67143; text-decoration: none;')
                a(style='color: #e67143; text-decoration: none;' href='mailto:support@jivescribe.com') support@jivescribe.com
              br
              span(style='color: #a8a5a5; text-align: center; font-size: 12px;') or call us
              span(style='color: #e67143; text-decoration: none;')
                a(style='color: #e67143; text-decoration: none;' href='#')  (+61 2) 8287 7314
            p(style='color: #a8a5a5; text-align: center; font-size: 12px;')
              | Jivescribe Pty Ltd
              br
              | 15/6 Meridian Place
